title: Bobby Surprises B-Teamer With Garth Tickets + The TV Catchphrase Draft + 60 Second Showdown Controversy

description:
Bobby saw a listener tying to win a contest on Twitter for Garth Brooks “Dive Bar” tickets so he called her up to surprise her! We do our TV Show Catchphrase game and there’s some controversy during our 60 Second Showdown with a final answer.
